\begin_layout Standard
Computing the gradient relies on the existence of partial derivatives of
 both 
\begin_inset Formula $\cost$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\sys$
\end_inset

.
 We assume that the partial derivatives of the cost function 
\begin_inset Formula $\cost$
\end_inset

